OL,6,FThe front of a house on Derbyshire
OL,7,FHill Road and part of the pavement was
OL,8,Fcordoned off.JAn area behind the
OL,9,FHorseshoe Garage on Ashtons Green
OL,10,FDrive was also cordoned off. An
OL,11,Fofficer was also seen guarding the
OL,12,Fback of the house where police were
OL,13,Ffocusing their attention on. A small
OL,14,Fcordon blocked off an opening which
OL,15,Falso lead to this area.JNeighbours in
OL,16,Fthe area said they were "shocked" to
OL,17,Fsee the amount of emergency service
OL,18,Fvehicles on the road yesterday
OL,19,Fafternoon. Later on in the morning, a
OL,20,Fmobile police van also attended the
OL,21,Fscene.
