OL,3,CMan in hospital after being shot in
OL,4,Cface
OL,6,FHouse-to-house enquiries were carried
OL,7,Fout yesterday. A spokesperson for the
OL,8,Fforce said a police scene will remain
OL,9,Fwhile detectives continue to
OL,10,Finvestigate the incident.
OL,12,FChief Inspector Tom Welch said: "This
OL,13,Fis a complex police investigation, and
OL,14,Four officers are still in the very
OL,15,Fearly stages of establishing the
OL,16,Fcircumstances of this incident.J"At
OL,17,Fthis stage of our ongoing
OL,18,Finvestigation we can confirm that a
OL,19,Ffirearm was shot in the area causing a
OL,20,Fserious facial injury to a man in his
OL,21,F30s.
